data.description: Nestled in a quaint, small subdivision on a large .64 acre lot this 4 Bedroom, 3 Full Bath home is ready for its new owner.  Kitchen has granite countertops, updated appliances, pantry with pull out shelves that provide for easy access, and a breakfast nook.  Luxury Vinyl Tile throughout the kitchen and living areas.  Separate formal dining and living space.  Living room boasts built in cabinets and a wood burning fireplace.  Spacious master bedroom and master bath with separate shower, corner tub, his and hers vanities, water closet, and a walk in closet with built in cabinets. The additional three bedrooms are all well sized and have lots of closet space. Relax with a cup of coffee on your front porch and entertain in the backyard and the newer outdoor patio area. Space for an outdoor kitchen, your favorite plants, and a swing! Lots of fresh paint throughout the house and very well maintained. Flood X and did not flood in 2016.  Denham Springs schools.  Conveniently located near the Denham Springs North Park and the Library, Juban Road shopping center and downtown Denham Springs, restaurants and much more!
